{"tid":306131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係屋企執舊收埋左二十年既玉戴，會否撞鬼？","createTime":"2017-07-02T09:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T09:31:20.000Z","uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1d34be0a4cc119a0bb4e978270ca6db6d466fbe","tid":306131,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:23:10.000Z","msg":"之前有晚心血來潮，覺得想定下驚，自己成日好緊張，之類<br />\n<br />\n所以叫屋企人係屋企角落執舊玉俾我戴下<br />\n<br />\n係二十年前親戚送，普通貨色，唔係貴野<br />\n<br />\n但果晚只係戴左一下就除左，因為覺得條繩觸感唔好<br />\n<br />\n之後果晚訓覺又淺眠狀態嚇醒左幾次<br />\n<br />\n關唔關事???<br />\n<br />\n同埋我個人一緊張，周圍的聲音會放大好多倍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n@(#$&amp;!(@&amp;#$(_!@#&amp;$( 有鬼呀！！！！！！"},{"pid":"b83e33781e1345852ef243dbad06060a2ae3226d","tid":306131,"uid":94457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:23:50.000Z","msg":"有無聽過攝魂玉？"},{"pid":"c5d5d3dc5d156bf44fda301de96b2fe9d290a6f1","tid":306131,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:25:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無聽過攝魂玉？</blockquote><br />\n我完全唔識呢d野<br />\n<br />\n舊玉係二十年前阿婆送<br />\n<br />\n一路冇戴二十年，收埋左係屋企衣櫃底下個細首飾盒<br />\n<br />\n因為自己太易緊張之類先想戴下定驚<br />\n<br />\n點知戴完果晚即刻驚 !@9#$&amp;(!#$&amp;("},{"pid":"06d0872804703b503d4941b89d4bbfaf9db369e4","tid":306131,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:27:06.000Z","msg":"塊玉咩色？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644d0815a5fdc6686f096068e6df1af1144a221f","tid":306131,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:27:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>塊玉咩色？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n普通綠色<br />\n<br />\n冇黑色<br />\n<br />\n我特登問過屋企人 戴玉會唔會出事<br />\n<br />\n應該唔會有事掛"},{"pid":"1ea89ab5248e5492921e04663781d15794a635e7","tid":306131,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit